      "raw_text": "An effort is being made by the\nchamber of commerce to secure a\nsettlement Of the millworkers' strike.\n\"A committee from that body. headed\nby President Goodal. attended Q\nmeeting Of the carpenters union last\nnight in an effort to secure their CO.\noperation in bringing about settle.\nment.\n\n\nPresident Goodal addressed the\ncarpenters. pointing out the evil re-\nsuits tp the city Of the constant agi-\ntation Of labor matters. and especial\n1y of the pending strike. He lament\ned the publicity which the labor stu\nalton in Spokane has obtained. point\ning out It's effect on trade and build\ning operations."
